<LegalDoc
  title="Refund Policy — Ivory Arc Travels"
  description="How refunds are handled for journeys arranged by Ivory Arc Travels."
  canonical="/legal/refund"
  heading="Refund Policy"
>
  <p>This policy explains how refunds work for journeys arranged by Ivory Arc Travels.</p>

  <h2>How refunds are calculated</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Refunds depend on the cancellation terms of the underlying suppliers (hotels, transport, guides, permits) at the time of cancellation.</li>
    <li>Amounts that suppliers treat as non-refundable cannot be returned.</li>
    <li>[State whether, and to what extent, the 10% coordination fee is refundable.]</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How refunds are paid</h2>
  <p>
    Approved refunds are returned to the original payment method via Razorpay, in INR. Processing
    times depend on your bank or card issuer.
  </p>

  <h2>Requesting a refund</h2>
  <p>
    To request a refund, contact us via our <a href="/contact">contact page</a> with your booking
    reference. See also our <a href="/legal/cancellation">cancellation policy</a>.
  </p>
</LegalDoc>
